        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1d238310-dd3a-4340-a5e3-cc2be003213b">
                Mr. A. V. Alexander
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1d238310-dd3a-4340-a5e3-cc2be003213b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-03-16/debates/f40b7ab7-e4d7-4b7f-b629-3178761d0294/NavyEstimates1939#contribution-1d238310-dd3a-4340-a5e3-cc2be003213b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would the hon. Gentleman mind telling me some of the characteristics of the new destroyers? Of what type are they to be?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1d238310-dd3a-4340-a5e3-cc2be003213b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-03-16/debates/f40b7ab7-e4d7-4b7f-b629-3178761d0294/NavyEstimates1939#contribution-1d238310-dd3a-4340-a5e3-cc2be003213b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
