                Major Lloyd George
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c49823c5-9601-4bd7-a0e8-ddb11e5245f2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
