            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Where is the Mercantile Marine to go?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c49823c5-9601-4bd7-a0e8-ddb11e5245f2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-03-16/debates/f40b7ab7-e4d7-4b7f-b629-3178761d0294/NavyEstimates1939#contribution-c49823c5-9601-4bd7-a0e8-ddb11e5245f2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
