<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-e4306a8d-99a1-4b05-a153-3e91c8b06aa5'>
            
<p class="">Navy is by failing to make proper provision for its maintenance and equipment. It is that proper provision which we ask the House to give us in these Estimates.</p>
